      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMMANCHE JACK (4) has a strong overall record having three wins and four places from eight starts including a last start third (25.39) over 450m at this track. Goes well from this draw. Happy to have him on top this line-up. ELITE ONE (2) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a 1.5 lengths second over 515m at Sandown, clocking 29.73. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from four starts. Expected to feature again. PAW WINKWORTH (6) has a strong record this trip with 11 wins and eight placings from 28 starts. Comes off a (22.40) win last time, scoring by 3.5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 400m at Warragul. Suited here and expected to run well. CALY JET (3) will need to find best form to compete.",
